<section id="hero-en" class="hero">
  <h1>Welcome to Mamu Minokamo’s Projects</h1>
  <p>I create tools that automate finance, AI workflows, and server operations using Python, Docker, and Excel.</p>
  <p>View my work, tutorials, and open-source contributions below.</p>
</section>

<section id="hero-ja" class="hero">
  <h1>プロジェクト一覧</h1>
  <p>PythonやDocker、Excelを使った自動化ツールや解説記事を公開しています。</p>
</section>

<section id="projects-en">
  <h2>My Projects</h2>
  <ul class="project-list">
    {% for project in site.projects %}
      <li class="project-card">
        {% if project.image %}
          <img src="{{ project.image }}" alt="{{ project.title }}">
        {% endif %}
        <h3><a href="{{ project.url | relative_url }}">{{ project.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ project.description }}</p>
        {% if project.github_url %}
          <p><a href="{{ project.github_url }}">View GitHub Repository</a></p>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

